data.description: Spacious 3BR 2.5BA townhome featuring an open floor plan with high ceilings, kitchen island and gas stove. Enjoy your primary suite with vaulted ceiling, soaking tub, step-in shower, double sinks and large walk-in closet. Interior freshly painted, new LVT flooring on main and enjoy A/C during the summer. Laundry on upper level with bedrooms. Attached large double car garage with extra outside parking. Cute covered porch in front. Beavercreek Elementary School. Close to Oregon City HS, Clackamas College, shopping, parks and I-205 for easy commuting.  HOA fee only $35 per month!
